<li>Smith, Kevin B. and Licari, Michael J. (2006) <i>Public Administration – Power and Politics in the Fourth Branch of Government</i>, LA: Roxbury Pub. Co. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-933220-04-X" title="Special:BookSources/1-933220-04-X">1-933220-04-X</a></li>
